snippet.title: Pregnant // Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the Game ► https://store.steampowered.com/app/1802460/Pregnant/

In this first-person horror experience you will solve puzzles while navigating the pitch black Reed forest. Armed with only your flashlight you are at the mercy of the forests inhabitants, with limited time to find your way before they find you and end your adventure.

Developed by Pregnant / @DavidStenssonDev
